VOTABLE.DESCRIPTION: User created table from data at the Extragalactic Distance Database: http://edd.ifa.hawaii.edu. VOTable is described at http://www.ivoa.net/Documents/latest/VOT.html
VOTABLE.INFO: SELECT pgc.PGC , klvgdb.`ID`,klvgdb.`Name`,klvgdb.`RA_J2000`,klvgdb.`DecJ2000` from pgc LEFT JOIN klvgdb on (pgc.PGC=klvgdb.PGC) LEFT JOIN kleda on (pgc.PGC=kleda.PGC) WHERE (coalesce(klvgdb.`ID`,klvgdb.`Name`,klvgdb.`RA_J2000`,klvgdb.`DecJ2000`) IS NOT NULL)

FIELD.name: PGC_ID
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: The Catalogue of Principal Galaxies (PGC) Number

FIELD.name: ID
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ID from catalog Local Volume Galaxy Data Base

FIELD.name: Name
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Common name from catalog Local Volume Galaxy Data Base

FIELD.name: RA_J2000
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Right Ascension, epoch J2000 from catalog Local Volume Galaxy Data Base

FIELD.name: DecJ2000
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Declination, epoch J2000 from catalog Local Volume Galaxy Data Base
